onMouseOut="nd();">1</A>
85/84 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>, according to the chronology of Suetonius, which makes the year of Caesar's birth 100 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> The arguments in favour of 102 are however very strong.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


