"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">63</A>
For carrying his statue among those of the gods.

	<DIV CLASS="mynote">
	<P CLASS="b0 a0">
Thayer's Note: For comprehensive details and sources on the opening procession at the circus games, and the special "chariot and litter" involved ("litter and chariot", actually — <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">tensam et ferculum</SPAN>) see
		<A HREF="
